#Title
Cities list contains duplicate cities

#Environment
Pixel 3a, Android 9
Environment independent

#Steps to reproduce
1. Run the application
2. Wait until cities list is loaded
3. Type 'porto' into search field
4. Wait until search result is ready
5. Find 'Porto, ES' city

#Expected Result
Cities list doesn't contain duplicate cities
All cities are distinguishable

#Actual Result
Cities list contains cities with the same name and country

#Severity/Priority
Medium/Medium

#Notes
List contains three Porto, ES cities.
Two nodes are the same city:
    Duplicates should be removed.
Third node is another city with the same name and country:
    The node name should be more descriptive(region or coordinates can be added)